{"title":"badhair","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3098","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>有 N(1 ≤n ≤ 80,000) 头很关注自己发型的牛 站在一排 ，望着同一个方向。 每头牛都 有一个高度 hi (1 ≤ hi ≤ 1,000,000,000) 。每头牛只能看见自己前方比自己矮的的发型。请计算出所有牛能看到的发型总数</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行个整数： N<br>接下来 N行：每一个整数，表示第 i头牛的高度 hi</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个整数，表示所有的牛能看到发型总。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>6<br>10<br>3<br>7<br>4<br>12<br>2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1 ≤ N  ≤ 80,000</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}